@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor User

rectangle "COLORS Web Application" {
  usecase "Log In" as UC_Login
  usecase "Search Color" as UC_Search
  usecase "Add Color" as UC_Add
  usecase "Log Out" as UC_Logout
  usecase "Validate Session\n(read cookie)" as UC_Session
}

User --> UC_Login
User --> UC_Search
User --> UC_Add
User --> UC_Logout

UC_Search .> UC_Session : <<include>>
UC_Add .> UC_Session : <<include>>
UC_Logout .> UC_Session : <<include>>

note right of UC_Login
User enters username and password.
System authenticates with Login.php.
On success, system stores cookie and
redirects to color.html.
end note

note right of UC_Session
color.html calls readCookie() on load.
If cookie is invalid/missing,
user is redirected to index.html.
end note
@enduml